[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "ねえウィルベル。さっきアトリエで「亜空の道」の\n話を聞いちゃったんだけどさー",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "もっと色々教えてよ！\nやりたいことがあるから！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "あんた、また変なこと考えてるでしょ。\n「亜空の道」はそんな軽いもんじゃないのよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "だってさ、離れた場所を一瞬で繋げられるんだよ？\nリディーのお菓子をこっそり盗み放題！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "はぁ……発想が子どもなのよ、あんたは",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "それに、そんな便利なもんじゃないわよ？\n好き勝手色んな場所に繋げられるものじゃないんだから",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "ユーディー",
		"romanized_name": "Judie",
		"model_path_hash": "2697025160672431728",
		"text": "……あ、ウィルベル、スール。\nここに居たんだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2032894617718182411",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "ユーディット、どうしたの？　\nなんか元気ないじゃない",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "ユーディー",
		"romanized_name": "Judie",
		"model_path_hash": "2697025160672431728",
		"text": "またキースさんが勝手にどこか行っちゃって……\nあたしが買い物してる間に",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2032894617718182411",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "……ねえ、ユーディットさん。\nそんなキースさんにやり返したいって思わない？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "ユーディー",
		"romanized_name": "Judie",
		"model_path_hash": "2697025160672431728",
		"text": "やり返す？　どうやって？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2032894617718182411",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "「亜空の道」っていう便利なものがあるんだって！\nそれがあれば、離れた所からイタズラし放題！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "だから、好き勝手色んな場所に\n繋げられるものじゃないんだって",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "そんな不可能を可能にするのが、錬金術だよ！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "……本当にできる？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "お母さんとの約束その１！\n「やる前から無理って諦めない！」",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "あたしがやるって言ったら、できるまでやるんだから！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "……いいわ、やってやろうじゃない。\nあのオジサン、前から一泡吹かせてやりたかったしね！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "ユーディー",
		"romanized_name": "Judie",
		"model_path_hash": "2697025160672431728",
		"text": "えぇ！？　あたしは別に怒ってないけど……\nでも、ちょっと面白そうかも",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2032894617718182411",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "イクセル",
		"romanized_name": "Yksel",
		"model_path_hash": "8416193151802436544",
		"text": "おいおい、また悪ガキどもが何か企んでるのか？　\n顔に書いてあるぜ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8827427841789589118",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "何をー！　君、あたしたちのこと\nガキって言えるような歳じゃないじゃん！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "まあまあ、イクセルも聞いてよ。「亜空の道」の技術が\nあれば、世界中の食材調達し放題なんだって",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "イクセル",
		"romanized_name": "Yksel",
		"model_path_hash": "8416193151802436544",
		"text": "なに！？　それ本当か？　……よし、俺も協力するぜ！　\n新しい味のためなら悪だくみも悪くねぇな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8827427841789589118",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "ユーディー",
		"romanized_name": "Judie",
		"model_path_hash": "2697025160672431728",
		"text": "みんなノリノリだね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2032894617718182411",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "でもさ、今キースさんがどこにいるか分かんないと、\n「亜空の道」も繋げられないよね",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "ユーディー",
		"romanized_name": "Judie",
		"model_path_hash": "2697025160672431728",
		"text": "まずはその方法を検討するところからかな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "2032894617718182411",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "おう、イクセル。いつもの頼む",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "イクセル",
		"romanized_name": "Yksel",
		"model_path_hash": "8416193151802436544",
		"text": "おっさん！　あいよ、今すぐ持ってくるぜ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8827427841789589118",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 28,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "おい、ちょうどいいところに居たな。\nお前らも暇なら手伝え。荷物運びだ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 29,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "えー！？　今いいところだったのに……",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 30,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "なんかイクセルの奴、大量の包みを持ってきたけど……\nあれなに？",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 31,
		"localized_name": "イクセル",
		"romanized_name": "Yksel",
		"model_path_hash": "8416193151802436544",
		"text": "行けば分かるって。\nということで、荷物運びよろしくな",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8827427841789589118",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 32,
		"localized_name": "スール",
		"romanized_name": "Suelle",
		"model_path_hash": "3072540865312949120",
		"text": "あーん……まあ、いっか。\n荷物運びついでにキースさん探しもできるかもだし",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "8906082768242880907",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 33,
		"localized_name": "ランツェ",
		"romanized_name": "Lanze",
		"model_path_hash": "845404123422268284",
		"text": "おい、変なこと考えてる顔だな。\n余計なことするなよ",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "5409134969144639524",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 34,
		"localized_name": "ウィルベル",
		"romanized_name": "Wilbell",
		"model_path_hash": "4415481844247416114",
		"text": "ふふ、どうなるかはお楽しみってことで！",
		"voice_file": "",
		"still_path_hash": "1953533162853626950",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]